"""
Abstract superclass of all numeric types (SmallInteger, BigInteger, Float).
Concrete arithmetic and comparison operations are defined by subclasses.
Number inherits comparison-derived methods (`max:`, `min:`, `between:and:`)
from Magnitude.
"""
Number subclass: Magnitude

  """Type test — true for all numbers.

  ```example
  42 isNumber
  ```
  """
  method: isNumber ^<Boolean> [ ^true ]
